<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; color: #333;">
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <h1 style="color: #4CAF50; margin-bottom: 5px;">üéâ Welcome to HopeLink!</h1>
    <h2 style="color: #333; margin-top: 0;">Your Organization Has Been Approved</h2>
  </div>

  <div style="background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p>Hello {{representativeName}},</p>
    
    <p>We're excited to inform you that your organization <strong>{{organizationName}}</strong> has been approved on HopeLink.</p>
    
    {{#if password}}
    <div style="background-color: #fff; border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50; padding: 10px 15px; margin: 15px 0;">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #4CAF50;">Your Login Credentials</h3>
      <p style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
      <p style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong>Password:</strong> <code style="background: #e8e8e8; padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 3px;">{{password}}</code></p>
    </div>
    {{/if}}
    
    <p>You can now log in to your account and start managing your organization's profile and opportunities.</p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/login" 
         style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold;">
        Login to Your Account
      </a>
    </div>
    
    {{#if password}}
    <div style="background-color: #fff8e1; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 10px 15px; margin: 15px 0;">
      <p style="color: #ff6f00; margin: 5px 0; font-weight: bold;">‚ö†Ô∏è Security Notice</p>
      <p style="margin: 5px 0;">For your security, please change your password after your first login.</p>
